name: 卡琳·米歇尔森
name_full: 卡琳·米歇尔森 Karin Michelsen

last_movies.title: 深夜加油站遇见大逃杀

introduction: Karin Michelsen is a versatile actress having played a range of characters from femme fatale to white trash heroines in horror-movies, various female parts in pilot tv series and a psykriatic patient in forum theatre around Denmark. She is also quite adept at playing humor as she has done in childrens television for Denmark's national television.
